      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "3cae15c6ef130eaa",
      "text": "From 1997 to 2004 the congress also hosted the annual German Lockpicking Championships. 2005 was the first year the Congress lasted four days instead of three and lacked the German Lockpicking Championships."
